*   **Died** 28 August 1648 (aged 34–35), [Colchester, Essex](/Colchester,_Essex)
*   **Resting place** [St Giles's Church, Colchester](/Churches_in_Colchester) (now St Giles Masonic Centre)
*   **Alma mater** [Christ's College, Cambridge](/Christ%27s_College,_Cambridge)

